{
  "stem": "18960.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 402.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went to Jewish school called-- it was-- the-- the name of the school of Professor Leon Sternberg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But being the-- the director of the school was-- was a-- a Professor Blatt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So colloquially, it was called the Blatt's Gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's where I spent the next six years of my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- the first four years are still till the outbreak of the war was gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then when the-- when the war broke out and the Russians came, it was still the same school and I continued with two more years, the lyceum, where I graduated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I was even matriculated at-- into medical school in Lwow a-- a week before the-- the Russo-German war broke out in 1941.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And being I was a top student, I was accepted without the entrance exam.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Elementary school years were 1929, when I turned six, 1929 till about the year of 1935.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1935, I started high school gymnasium, till 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Four years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I ended with-- gymnasium was four years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I ended in-- in 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in 1941-- 19-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In 1939, in the fall was after-- right after the outbreak of the war, when the Russians came, I started lyceum.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The same school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Until 1941.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "June 1941.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At the end of the school year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Schodnica.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those memorable days of-- of my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] See, I'm a little emotional.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] When we sat down at the table, the Sabbath table Friday night, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] my grandfather was sitting at-- at the head of the table.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Next to him, my-- my grandmother, then my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And me and my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
